              "text": "We test for harmful outputs. Bias, toxicity, misinformation.",
              "delay": 1.4
            },
            {
              "from": "elena",
              "text": "But we don't test for subtle persuasion. Outputs that are factually correct but systematically framed to shape behavior.",
              "delay": 2.0
            },
            {
              "from": "elena",
              "text": "I flagged it. I wrote a twelve-page internal report.",
              "delay": 1.4
            },
            {
              "from": "elena",
              "text": "The response was: 'This is outside the scope of current evaluation priorities.'",
              "delay": 1.5
            },
            {
              "from": "elena",
              "text": "Signed by Maxwell's office directly.",
              "delay": 1.2
            }
